{
  "texts": [
    "However, setting the a/r ratio to 2 or 4 potentially enhanced results, signifying a stronger influence from QLoRA layers on the base model.",
    "However, this adjustment led to a decline in the quality of explanations.",
    "The improvement could be attributed to the model's low intrinsic dimensionality.",
    "Despite having many parameters, the effective dimensionality of the model's learned representations is low.",
    "Consequently, after conducting several experiments, the best-performing model regarding word puzzles aligns with this concept."
  ]
}